<div class="space-y-4 mb-6 relative">

  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#004865]">
    本を検索
  </h3>

  <div>
    <div class="relative">
      <input
        type="text"
        placeholder="タイトル・著者名・ISBN"
        class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2
               focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#004865]"
        data-book-search-target="input"
        data-action="input->book-search#search"
      >
    </div>

    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
      検索結果から本を選択すると、取得できる範囲で本の情報が自動入力されます。
    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-4 hidden relative z-30"
      data-book-search-target="selected"
    >
      <div
        class="relative w-full p-4 text-left
               flex gap-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-md
               bg-gray-50"
      >
        <button
          type="button"
          class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2
                 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600
                 cursor-pointer p-1"
          data-action="click->book-search#clearSelectedBook"
        >
          ✕
        </button>

        <img
          src=""
          alt=""
          class="w-12 h-16 object-cover rounded"
          data-book-search-target="selectedCover"
        />

        <div class="flex-1">
          <div
            class="font-semibold text-gray-900"
            data-book-search-target="selectedTitle"
          ></div>

          <div
            class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1"
            data-book-search-target="selectedAuthor"
          ></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ▼ 検索結果（オーバーレイ） -->
  <ul
    class="absolute left-0 right-0 top-full mt-2
           border border-gray-200 rounded-md divide-y
           bg-white shadow-lg z-20 hidden
           max-h-64 overflow-y-auto"
    data-book-search-target="results"
  ></ul>

  <div class="border-b border-gray-300 pt-4"></div>
</div>
